{"tid":813514,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"DBS 點先做到0.56 一里?","createTime":"2018-09-10T13:20:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T04:35:41.000Z","uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0c7ab0974a7853c10d2416d8c28223a97b00e268","tid":813514,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:20:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.dbs.com.hk/personal-zh/credit-cards/black-welcome-mc-tnc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dbs.com.hk%2Fpersonal-zh%2Fcredit-cards%2Fblack-welcome-mc-tnc.html&d=nxdefjDRBkq1KAagcTCPl%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=306b6ac0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dbs.com.hk/personal-zh/credit-cards/black-welcome-mc-tnc.html</a><br />\n睇咗成篇嘢幾次, 都唔知點樣0.56一里. <br />\n1:要求話開咭2個月內達到以下要求? 係咪即係5000蚊?<br />\n5000蚊有5000里? 當你換5000里時佢就會送4000里? 5000蚊 / 9000里 = 5.56<br />\n2:但係又話&quot; 到eSHOP用DBS$以單一交易兌換5,000 Avios里數或以上（按現時適用的里數兌換比率DBS$48 = 1,000里數計算，即須將不少於DBS$240兌換為Avios里數）&quot; <br />\n要用DBS$240 換 5000里. 但係碌125蚊先有DBS$ 1, DBS$咁240咪即係要碌30000?<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打可以請教下, 到底係點計? 好亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79ad9a4c17bad8f37d72e4f20d1ddd63157fa46","tid":813514,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T04:35:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}